casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Deondre Kenyetta ELIE, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158785
COA: 345591 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 30, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the October 31, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
